    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per the MRL 2 assessment matrix. Quantitative validation demonstrates NIH prediction error of 8.3% MAE against experimental data, within the 15% acceptance band. Mesh convergence GCI of 1.7% confirms numerical accuracy. The CFD model is assessed as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Regulatory submission package approved for filing.",
